        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/all-things-are-connected.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/all-things-are-connected.html",
            "title": "All Things are Connected",
            "summary": "The concept for this sketch was to show the unseen connection between&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00428_.png\" data-size=\"1192x1240\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00428_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"799\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/20241108_201720.jpg\" data-size=\"1195x1240\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/20241108_201720-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"797\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00427_.png\" data-size=\"1192x1240\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00427_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"799\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00408_.png\" data-size=\"1192x1240\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00408_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"799\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00164_.png\" data-size=\"1024x1024\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00164_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>The concept for this sketch was to show the unseen connection between all planes of existence. Each shares a part with everything in the universe of matter and beyond. The woman in the foreground represents the unseen, the background was one of my living spaces many decades ago. This was extremely challenging to try and get AI to create a cohesive image in just one go.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/32/Qwen_Edit_2511_00429_.png",
            "author": {
