            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-18T21:08:39-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-18T21:08:39-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/angelic-love.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/angelic-love.html",
            "title": "Angelic Love",
            "summary": "I created this sketch while I was out of state painting the&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00488_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00488_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/scan0002.jpg\" data-size=\"1660x2201\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/scan0002-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1018\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00487_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00487_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00486_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00486_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00485_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00485_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00484_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00484_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00483_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00483_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00482_.png\" data-size=\"1160x1536\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_00482_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1017\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>I created this sketch while I was out of state painting the backside of a Lowes for a contract paint company. The men I drove to the job wanted to go to a gentleman's club after we were done with the job and one of the dancer's inspired me to draw this. The AI version is the complete scene of what I saw which was her soul, and the background represents the place we both where in. Even in the darkest of places beauty can shine bright : ) </p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/31/Qwen_Edit_2511_00486_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Rough Sketch",
