                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-18T20:30:28-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-18T20:40:03-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/imagine-you-are-a-day.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/imagine-you-are-a-day.html",
            "title": "Imagine you are a Day",
            "summary": "This was a poem I made for my mother when she was&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/100_1273.JPG\" data-size=\"1932x2576\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/100_1273-thumbnail.JPG\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01779_.png\" data-size=\"1544x1152\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01779_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"573\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01763_.png\" data-size=\"1472x1104\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01763_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01756_.png\" data-size=\"1472x1104\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01756_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01750_.png\" data-size=\"1472x1104\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01750_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"576\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01736_.png\" data-size=\"1328x1328\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01736_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"768\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01734_.png\" data-size=\"1544x1152\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01734_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"573\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This was a poem I made for my mother when she was sick, I had her send me an image years later because so much time had passed I forgot what I wrote. I used AI to see how well it would keep the text it could see and make an interesting image to go with the poem. Imagine we found messages like this as we explore the universe.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/30/Qwen_Edit_2511_01781_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Poem",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-17T20:08:49-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-17T20:09:13-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/he-is-a-fungi.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/he-is-a-fungi.html",
            "title": "He is a fungi : )",
            "summary": "He is a fungi, a mushroom man standing outside his home. I&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"3\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/scan0081.jpg\" data-size=\"1579x2113\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/scan0081-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1028\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01853_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01853_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01850_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01850_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01839_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01839_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01838_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01838_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01833_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01833_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01831_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01831_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01829_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01829_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01828_.png\" data-size=\"1088x1496\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/gallery/Qwen_Edit_2511_01828_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1056\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>He is a fungi, a mushroom man standing outside his home. I was exploring different methods of creating an image by changing the math used to form the image during the process an AI goes thru in a comfyui environment, using a starting image which was one of my old drawings.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/29/Qwen_Edit_2511_01831_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Rough Sketch",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-17T19:56:46-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-17T19:56:46-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/graffiti-presto-swirl.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/graffiti-presto-swirl.html",
            "title": "Graffiti Presto Swirl",
            "summary": "Every artist at one point or another has done some form of&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/28/gallery/ComfyUI_00453_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/28/gallery/ComfyUI_00453_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/28/gallery/scan0022.jpg\" data-size=\"1648x2250\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/28/gallery/scan0022-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1049\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>Every artist at one point or another has done some form of graffiti art style. I choose Presto a very long time ago as my graffiti name to develop and design with. When you try to draw the same word over and over trying to improve, or just to create a new version, this process is the equivalent to going to a gym to workout your body, except this process is a workout for your mind. I am excited every time I give AI one of my original works of art, sitting with anticipation waiting less then a minute to see a simple line artwork turned into a full color piece. I did not give much guidance to AI to learn how it thinks before taking full control of the direction. </p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/28/ComfyUI_00453_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Graffiti",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-06T01:13:04-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-06T01:18:30-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/money-monster.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/money-monster.html",
            "title": "Money Monster",
            "summary": "Time has not been kind to my original black and white drawing.",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/20251106_051321.jpg\" data-size=\"3024x4032\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/20251106_051321-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1024\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/ComfyUI_00619_.png\" data-size=\"1240x1656\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/ComfyUI_00619_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1026\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/ComfyUI_00617_.png\" data-size=\"1240x1656\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/ComfyUI_00617_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1026\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/ComfyUI_00616_.png\" data-size=\"1240x1656\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/gallery/ComfyUI_00616_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1026\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>Time has not been kind to my original black and white drawing. I will have to try a full restoration using AI. I did use AI for the section that was okay. I gave it minimal guidance to what to create because i wanted to see how it interpreted the design. As you can see from the results it got the idea I was trying to convey with my design.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/27/ComfyUI_00617_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-06T00:35:59-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-06T00:35:59-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/drawing-my-friends.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/drawing-my-friends.html",
            "title": "Drawing my Friends",
            "summary": "This is a fun black and white sketch surreal style. I used&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/26/gallery/ComfyUI_00454_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/26/gallery/ComfyUI_00454_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/26/gallery/scan0023.jpg\" data-size=\"1601x2091\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/26/gallery/scan0023-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1003\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is a fun black and white sketch surreal style. I used AI testing how it would interpret the shapes, people and creatures in the sketch. I gave it minimal guidance to see what is thought it was seeing. I find AI fun and intriguing because it adds a step to the creative process, in the past when I got stuck on a piece of design, I would have to wait till inspiration hit, now AI as a tool can speed up this process.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/26/ComfyUI_00454_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Rough Sketch",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-06T00:18:32-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-06T00:18:32-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/man-with-fish-bowl.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/man-with-fish-bowl.html",
            "title": "Man with Fish Bowl",
            "summary": "This is black and white sketch that is one part of a&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/gallery/ComfyUI_00455_.png\" data-size=\"1224x1688\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/gallery/ComfyUI_00455_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1059\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/gallery/scan0015.jpg\" data-size=\"1590x2086\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/gallery/scan0015-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"1008\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/gallery/rave-world-lg.jpg\" data-size=\"770x367\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/gallery/rave-world-lg-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"366\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is black and white sketch that is one part of a large fine art painting I made. This is a surreal piece that I gave to AI to see what it could do with a surreal image. this AI image had its own colorful interpretation of the shapes and how they related. i have included the fine art painting that this sketch was part of.</p>",
            "image": "https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/25/ComfyUI_00455_.png",
            "author": {
                "name": "Rudy"
            },
            "tags": [
                   "Sketch",
                   "Fine Art Painting",
                   "AI Image"
            ],
            "date_published": "2026-07-05T23:12:38-04:00",
            "date_modified": "2026-07-05T23:14:18-04:00"
        },
        {
            "id": "https://rudytrnka.com/friends-forever.html",
            "url": "https://rudytrnka.com/friends-forever.html",
            "title": "Friends Forever",
            "summary": "This is a not the best version of this drawing I made&hellip;",
            "content_html": "<div class=\"gallery-wrapper\"><div class=\"gallery\" data-is-empty=\"false\" data-translation=\"Add images\" data-columns=\"2\">\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/ComfyUI_00438_.png\" data-size=\"1768x1168\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/ComfyUI_00438_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"507\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/ComfyUI_00436_.png\" data-size=\"1768x1168\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/ComfyUI_00436_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"507\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/ComfyUI_00434_.png\" data-size=\"1768x1168\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/ComfyUI_00434_-thumbnail.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"768\" height=\"507\"></a></figure>\n<figure class=\"gallery__item\"><a href=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/girl-with-dog-lg.jpg\" data-size=\"598x396\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://rudytrnka.com/media/posts/24/gallery/girl-with-dog-lg-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"598\" height=\"396\"></a></figure>\n</div></div>\n<p>This is a not the best version of this drawing I made a long time ago, the digital copy has a lot of extra noise, but you can see my style, I added a touch of whimsy to the picture I drew this portrait of a friend and her dog. The color versions are the AI versions I made while seeing how much additional whimsy I could add while maintaining the original black and white drawing style. I also experimented with extending the original image by making the size of the AI image larger then the input.</p>",
